  "3059240": {
    "name": "Space Shooter",
    "steam_appid": 3059240,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059240/extras/3e40ee0bca3adae7cdb54ef79b87068a.avif?t=1732708727\" width=616 height=205 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome aboard!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Here, we gain points by destroying meteors. Some are big, some are small. Try your best to destroy as many as you can and avoid destroying our ship! This is a wave-type game, where the more you play, the more difficult the game becomes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059240/extras/a303d1691066547360ae117f44d0c217.avif?t=1732708727\" width=616 height=205 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Scoreboard</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is a scoreboard where you can beat your own score or, if you're as good as you think, try to get the TOP 1 spot! The hardest thing is to maintain the TOP 1 spot, so be careful and pay attention to not fall down the ranks!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059240/extras/3af49e23191d4bffad83954a5af7ac1b.avif?t=1732708727\" width=616 height=205 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Power-Ups</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game has some power-ups that have a chance to spawn randomly every time you pass a wave. Discover them all! (It took a long time to make them...)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059240/extras/81e3be58f23460565a080ea5f4b22fff.avif?t=1732708727\" width=616 height=205 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Planned Updates<br>  </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Events </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > More Languages </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Game Feel - In Development </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Mobile Release</p></li></ul>",
